Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:38.72,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,What is Alolan N— {The little gap is kinda awkward, bit of a shame they didn't edit Kuwashi's line and cut in just a little sooner, or have the host's seiyuu read out the full name and cut him off in the editing. - Toa}
