Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.82,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Long time, no see-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.09,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:16.68,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,But of course! This man is none other than \N the producer of Alolan Detective Laki-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.40,Main,George,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.32,Main,George,0,0,0,,I’m George Charanpino! \N So pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.75,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You make \N Alolan Detective Laki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.79,Main,Lilie & Suiren,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.18,Main,George,0,0,0,,By the way, my dear Rotom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.24,Main,George,0,0,0,,What brings you to Alola TV today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.98,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,My friend was participating \N in a quiz show-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.94,Main,George,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! I thought for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:43.09,Main,George,0,0,0,,...that you’d decided you wanted \N to be in Alolan Detective Laki again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.34,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,But he lost in the preliminaries, \N so we’re just about to leave-roto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.08,Main,George,0,0,0,,I see. That’s a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.29,Main,George,0,0,0,,In that case... \N They’re shooting a drama nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.35,Main,George,0,0,0,,Care to come and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.87,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What?! Yeah, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:55.81,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Can we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.72,Main,George,0,0,0,,Of course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.94,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Think we’ll get to meet a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.98,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,I’ll be taking \N plenty of photos-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.28,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Don’t do anything \N too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.07,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.77,Main,George,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.79,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What? Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.30,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Ah! That’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.30,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Koiking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.22,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,I-I-It’s Li’l Koi-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.30,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,W-Wh-What?!
