Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.72,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Koiking child actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:46.85,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,The ongoing TV drama that Li’l Koi stars in, \N “A Tiny Koiking’s Melody”...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:51.69,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,...is a super high-profile series, and it’s said that \N Li’l Koi’s acting has moved all of Alola to tears! {Kinda wanna suggest "critics rave" in place of "it's said" but that's probably be too loose. - Toa}{Yeah that's a bit too much. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.81,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You sure know \N a lot about this, Kaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:56.71,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,My little sister, Hoshi, \N is a huge Li’l Koi fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.17,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Li’l Koi’s acting during \N the crying scenes is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.96,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Like the acting during the scene \N where he was reunited with his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:17.85,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,His adorable high voice there really \N tugged at your heartstrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:22.40,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,And unlike other Koiking, \N Li’l Koi doesn’t {\i1}just{\i0} flop around when using Splash...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.28,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,He flops around while {\i1}spinning{\i0}-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:28.00,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,He became popular because of \N how cute he looks when doing that-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,He can do that?! Awesome! {RULE BREAKER! - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.70,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I can’t believe I get to watch \N Li’l Koi’s acting up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.75,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,You don’t get chances like these often!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.45,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Rotom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.09,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Take some pictures. For Hoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.67,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,You got it-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.26,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.16,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,No unauthorized photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.76,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,I’m sorry-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.85,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Talk about intense...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.83,Main,George,0,0,0,,She’s Li’l Koi’s manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.20,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.58,Main,George,0,0,0,,The one who looks after Li’l Koi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.40,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,He’s got people looking after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.79,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Li’l Koi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:10.47,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,It’s time to film the scene where you part ways \N with your friend, Youngoose. Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:17.58,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,We’re just about to start filming, \N so everyone please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.26,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Looks like they’re starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.63,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Listen up, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.94,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,You’d better burn Li’l Koi’s acting \N into your retinas, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.46,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:30.40,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Well then, let’s go! \N Let us hear your beautiful voice, Li’l Koi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.68,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Ready, and... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.45,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Hoarse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.29,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.87,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Li’l Koi? \N Let’s try that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.68,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,His body just glowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.97,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.26,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Sure you didn’t just \N sense his superstar aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:20.58,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Li’l Koi, let’s hear \N your usual, cute voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.83,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Let’s try one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.87,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with Li’l Koi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.74,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Does he have \N a cold or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:39.76,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.05,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,We need a little break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.27,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Li’l Koi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.65,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Oh, w-wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Think Li’l Koi’s not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.71,Main,George,0,0,0,,Oh, my! I’m afraid \N I’ll have to take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.81,Main,George,0,0,0,,I’ve got a shoot to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.57,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you very much!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.87,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,George, we’ve got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.12,Main,George,0,0,0,,Why are you so riled up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:08.61,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,The lead actors from ThreeDri \N just said they can’t make it to the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.40,Main,George,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:13.53,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,Apparently, their last job was \N a shoot in the Sinnoh Region,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.47,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,but then a Yukinooh and \N Yukimenoko started fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.41,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,and they caused a blizzard that’s \N grounded their flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:23.00,Main,Rinka the Pokénchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,We have to film today, or there’s no way \N we’ll have the program ready for its air date!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.11,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,George, if we don’t do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:30.42,Main,Ken'ichi the Pokenchi Cameo Actor,0,0,0,,we’ll have to do a rerun of “Alola King! \N The Royal Battle to Calm Down Archeos” instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.30,Main,The Pokechi Cameo Actors,0,0,0,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.49,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Sounds like there’s trouble-roto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.18,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.04,Main,George,0,0,0,,Good! No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:46.29,Main,George,0,0,0,,Nothing gets your blood rushing more \N than some unexpected trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.90,Main,George,0,0,0,,Moments of crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.91,Main,George,0,0,0,,...present a grand opportunity \N to create something new!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.16,Main,George,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.37,Main,George,0,0,0,,That’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.05,Main,George,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.96,Main,George,0,0,0,,Let’s make a drama with you three \N as the main characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.80,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.81,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Main characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.24,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,What’s that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.20,Main,George,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:18.51,Main,George,0,0,0,,The program we were going to film \N stars three girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:22.30,Main,George,0,0,0,,And we want these adorable Pokémon \N to appear alongside you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:28.02,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,But my only acting experience \N is being in the School play...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.15,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,You would be better off \N finding someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.48,Main,George,0,0,0,,No, we want you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.82,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’d like to try! It sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.69,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Well then, I’m joining, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.60,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,What about you, Lilie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.37,Main,George,0,0,0,,It’s your chance \N to meet a new you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.08,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,V-Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.34,Main,George,0,0,0,,That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.72,Main,George,0,0,0,,Let’s get right to rehearsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.43,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I can’t believe they all agreed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:57.26,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,George sure makes some \N pretty bold decisions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.37,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,This is far too bold, \N even for him-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.68,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lucky them! \N I wanna be on TV, too!{Indeed. If only there had been some sort of televised event which Satoshi had participated in. Like, some sort of battling tournament or something. Maybe even something where he made it to the finals in an epic battle with his one-of-a-kind super awesome ninja frog. But alas... -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.09,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.94,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,We’re starting filming again. \N Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.96,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Is Li’l Koi all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.94,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,He’s fine now! \N Aren’t you, Li’l Koi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.48,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Li’l Koi, just do it like \N you normally do, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.16,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Ready, and... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.55,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,He glowed! \N He definitely glowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:59.63,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,H-He evolved into Gyarados...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.03,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Li’l Koi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.66,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Wait, Li’l Koi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.65,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Let’s chase after him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.00,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.28,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Li’l Koi, it’s me! \N Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.91,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Guess today’s shoot is canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.37,Main,George,0,0,0,,All right, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:29.48,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.33,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.63,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Yes... You’re fantastic! \N So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:44.36,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Musabarbara, this audition will change \N your very acting life, meow! {Is "(acting )career" in place of "acting life" inaccurate? - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.76,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,I’m quite aware, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.62,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,So, what sort of work \N is this audition for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:53.88,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,A 12-hour drama made to commemorate \N the 55th anniversary of Alola TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.06,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,It’s a real high-profile piece, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.56,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.63,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.63,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of \N buff Pokémon here, don’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.59,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Well, it’s a high-profile piece \N after all, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.70,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Yup. A real high-profile piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:11.09,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Number 634, it’s your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:11.77,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.64,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,It’s finally your turn, \N Musabarbara, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.24,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,My Alola Region debut...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:25.15,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Act 1: The Star Arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:32.27,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,By the way, \N what kind of story is “ThreeDri”?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:38.29,Main,George,0,0,0,,The full title is \N “The Sparkling Trio is Alola DrinKyun”! {Is this a pun on "is (Alola) drinking"? - Toa}{I believe it's "Drink" plus "[strike]Moe Moe[/strike] Kyun". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.87,Main,George,0,0,0,,It doesn’t look like it’s \N ringing any bells for you, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.55,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,“Alola DrinKyun”? \N Never heard of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.87,Main,George,0,0,0,,They’re a group of three girls who \N protect the peace in Alola!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.95,Main,George,0,0,0,,Having a drink enables them \N to transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.56,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Oh, so they’re superheroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.27,Main,George,0,0,0,,That’s right. \N Here are your scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.07,Main,George,0,0,0,,And here’s one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.88,Main,George,0,0,0,,Now then, \N let’s get rehearsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.24,Main,George,0,0,0,,Ready, and... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.04,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Th-The thrill of pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.67,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The thrill of blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.57,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,N-No, wait, \N it was “twinkle,” not “thrill”!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.64,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,The radiance of yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:15.87,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Of yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:20.41,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sparkling trio unites! \N Alola DrinKyun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.13,Main,George,0,0,0,,Good! No worries! \N Let’s try that one more time! {RULE BREAKER! - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.88,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Didn’t you notice that \N he was about to evolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.79,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,I{\i1} did {\i0}think his whiskers \N had grown longer as of late...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.07,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,But I didn’t think it was \N because he was evolving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.02,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,My cute Li’l Koi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.52,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Not good! \N They’re filming something over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:47.15,Main,Ana,0,0,0,,Hi, this is Ana, coming to you \N from in front of Alola TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.27,Main,Ana,0,0,0,,It’s time for the afternoon—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.84,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.57,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.58,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,He went inside \N the building-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:04.71,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,We’re back for \N the Alola Pokémon Quiz’s final round!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:09.26,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuwashi only needs \N one more correct answer to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.59,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,And here comes the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.30,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Which Pokémon’s \N silhouette is this? {Original end time: 0:15:13.60 - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.71,Main,Kuwashi,0,0,0,,Tsutsukera! {Original start time: 0:15:13.60 - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.97,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuwashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.35,Main,Kuwashi,0,0,0,,Gyarados!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.60,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,And the answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.86,Main,MagikarpManager,0,0,0,,Wait, Li’l Koi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.07,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Correct! \N Congratulations!{How did he know. How dare this episode featuring the girls spontaneously getting a starring role in a PreCure ripoff while Satoshi and his friends chase after a child star who's gone through a very abrupt growth spurt not be 100% logical?! -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.83,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The thrill of pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.61,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The twinkle of blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.03,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,The radiance of yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:40.79,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sparkling trio unites! \N Alola DrinKyun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.26,Main,George,0,0,0,,Good! No worries! \N You’ve got this scene down perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.50,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.98,Main,George,0,0,0,,Now, let’s move on to the next scene.
