Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.78,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I can’t wait to see how it turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.30,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,This is so exciting!
